{"tid":1617832,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"19 fg 求屌醒","createTime":"2019-10-04T02:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T14:55:36.000Z","uid":221065,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3cf9eb41a681519ee62b2000faa39cbf7896d9","tid":1617832,"uid":221065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"19fg 眼見身邊好多同學仲做緊pt 或者hea緊， 我簡左份 人工高少少 但要番shift 既頹工做 又要企，但其實完全唔係自己鐘意既果行，其實番左一 兩個星期就想quit ， 但呢家已經差唔多3個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 但其實公司環境 同 同事都唔錯，唔知點算好，呢家認真咁諗就覺得自己想做hr果方面既工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我澳門人黎，賭場入既工 但有萬九，呢家少左後生入賭場做， 所以都算有前途， 但一轉行 就一切歸零，學到既野完全冇用<br />\n<br />\n同埋本身一直有keep著sd cv 搵 admin / hr 既工，但一直冇面試機會，月底就過3個月， 到時要90日通知期，唔知點算好，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7c4fb71bf4f07cff66ccf6cda951ceefffddce","tid":1617832,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"依家份工幾錢人工？"},{"pid":"f6103dd8af80ad63acefedd236173af205b213ae","tid":1617832,"uid":221065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"屋企唔算有好大經濟壓力，再加上以前讀大學時，有草到少少錢，同埋呢幾個月既人工，都夠頂裸辭後既一排生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實諗得可以裸辭係咪已經可以辭竹戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dac6d7e0e89c80182966c07344a0e2d2003f9e","tid":1617832,"uid":221065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa7c4fb71bf4f07cff66ccf6cda951ceefffddce","tid":1617832,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"依家份工幾錢人工？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:14:42.000Z","msg":"上面有打， $19,000"},{"pid":"4e92be3aaff53caed44ca2ec00a64aef6d8d5d9f","tid":1617832,"uid":221065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f6103dd8af80ad63acefedd236173af205b213ae","tid":1617832,"uid":221065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c